        "description": {
            "value": "<p>A giant pustule swells and explodes, coating everything around it in life-draining rot. Creatures and plants in the area take 6d6 poison damage and must attempt a Reflex save. Foliage and plant matter in the area damaged by the spell no longer provide cover.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target takes half damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target takes full damage and is @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target takes double damage, @Damage[(floor((@item.rank - 2)/2))d6[persistent,poison]] damage, and is @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 2}.</p><hr /><p><strong>Heightened (+2)</strong> The initial damage increases by 2d6, and the persistent damage on a critical failure increases by 1d6.</p>"
